entry.content:
My First Content

Hello Everyone. My name is Zabel Iqbal. I'm 28 years old self taught developer. I build a few web based projects for myself and clients around the globe. I'm located in Langkawi, Malaysia. 

Currently I actively running two business; Tapawfood and Extratera Solutions. Tapawfood is a Food Delivery Services company mainly focused at Langkawi and Extratera Solutions is a Web Development company focused on web based system development, mobile apps development and server provider. 

Let's talk about Extratera Solutions (ES) first. ES was establised on 2018
